        {
          "quote": "The paper investigates whether intratumoral delivery of an mRNA vaccine can create an interferon-rich inflammatory state that improves sensitivity to anti-PD-L1 therapy.",
          "line_ref": "L11"
        }
      ],
      "caveat": "Prospective randomized studies are required before clinical protocol changes are justified."
    }
  ]
